{"tid":2270770,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"聖誕節「和你shop」示威 年輕技工被控襲警  罪名不成立","createTime":"2020-11-04T07:56:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-04T09:28:53.000Z","uid":240362,"like":61,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":32,"replies":[{"pid":"c1c843ee96018d8b93fe6938cb1a6b91d6a6248d","tid":2270770,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T07:56:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/10973\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fyouarenotalonehk_live%2F10973&d=O3JFyT0uW1vU8ssvO3VcypB82cw%2Bhl0zMn8EQHxvzrU%3D&h=b63de13c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/youarenotalonehk_live/10973</a><br />\n<br />\n#觀塘裁判法院第八庭 <br />\n#梁少玲裁判官 <br />\n#裁決 #1225九龍灣<br />\n<br />\n黃(24)<br />\n控罪：襲擊在正當執行職務的警員<br />\n<br />\n❇️速報：罪名不成立❇️"},{"pid":"65b863dd9261181cbc2db67cbd469fe21fa5b4b9","tid":2270770,"uid":38737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T07:56:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d7feb2e37e2c63a9fafdd3cedad59bcaa68a28d","tid":2270770,"uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T07:57:04.000Z","msg":"年輕技工疑於去年聖誕節「和你shop」示威中，在九龍灣德福廣場警方離場時，用力撞向一名警長，令他即使身負逾40磅裝備，仍不慎退了一步。技工被控襲警罪，在觀塘裁判法院受審。辯方直指警長「賊喊捉賊」，自己先撞向被告，卻大叫「襲警」；又指從片段可見，警長經過被告時，主動踏前踩了他一腳。<br />\n<br />\n警長張基耀供稱，事發當晚9時許，警方解封德福廣場一期後，他與隊員便往地鐵站出口離去。走到Giordano Ladies店門外時，被告突然朝他踏前一步，再用右手大力撞向他的左膊，令他打橫退了一步。警長咬定被告「係蓄意撞埋嚟」，強調他執勤多年，「絕對分得清咩係意外咩係蓄意」。<br />\n<br />\n惟辯方大狀沈士文指出，事發時通道有不少空間，惟警長選擇靠左走近被告位置。當時被告只是「企喺到」，張經過被告時，卻主動踏前踩他及用左膊撞他；他自己不慎退了一步，卻大叫「襲警」。沈大狀續指，從控方截圖可見，事發一刻被告雙手垂下，而張的左腳踏在被告的右腳上；又指張在首份書面證供並無提及被告向他踏前一步，因為根本沒發生過。"},{"pid":"be69b1b561171a5508b27879448092972afb8284","tid":2270770,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65b863dd9261181cbc2db67cbd469fe21fa5b4b9","tid":2270770,"uid":38737,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T07:56:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T07:58:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/champagne.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ff85e429eea965d6bd3ea6d6ab007c84df1c5229","tid":2270770,"uid":6845,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T07:58:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7427e9d98d27e84938e3c8f8b9143a99acfb093","tid":2270770,"uid":271516,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T07:58:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e4583ee47a3db408a2cf15aefd0d0e548e1f12ca","tid":2270770,"uid":57205,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T07:59:52.000Z","msg":"告返隻狗傷人啦"},{"pid":"85c25dd6f1fb21bd7deb1565413929ddefd96a7d","tid":2270770,"uid":126731,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T08:00:15.000Z","msg":"D狗咬完你再屈你咬佢. 無片/紅官就入硬/<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6310fc6c5047b71a71ff012b94f03894c79418a5","tid":2270770,"uid":39796,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T08:01:10.000Z","msg":"作假口供 無後果<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee8dbcccf6f13893002c7ae8e5a15d5111314c09","tid":2270770,"uid":70786,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-04T08:01:48.000Z","msg":"張耀基<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"522441c6cdc0eb6fe12636bbd74d7aa2cf